# Subdivision Worker Packaging

`packages/subdivision-worker` is deployed as a Lambda container image.

The `Dockerfile` copies Python modules with an explicit `COPY` list. When adding,
renaming, or splitting Python modules in this package, update that `COPY` list so
the deployed Lambda image includes every imported local module.

Before considering a worker change complete, verify any new local imports are
present in `packages/subdivision-worker/Dockerfile`.
